S">Note that this building is within the scope limitations of the Standard =
NZS 3604:2011.&nbsp; NZS 3604:2011 is a cited means of
 compliance with building code clause B1 =E2=80=93 Structure for timber fra=
med buildings not requiring specific engineering design.&nbsp; This means t=
hat there is no legislative requirement for engaging a structural engineer =
for design requirements for the repair of this
 building.&nbsp; As such, any repair or construction carried out in accorda=
nce with the Standard is deemed to satisfy the relevant provisions of the b=
uilding code and the Building Act 2004.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-=
